<h2 class="bold font-l">Rejected Vampire</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Apparently, being an actual vampire doesn't help you get the part. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YourCostumeNeedsWork" class='trope-example-link'>Your Costume Needs Work</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
